# cache22 health check: critical services.
#
# List one systemd unit per line. After boot, if any unit listed here is not
# active across three consecutive boots, cache22 rolls back to the previous
# deployment. Blank lines and text after '#' are ignored.
#
# With nothing listed, the health check does nothing and never rolls back. Add
# the services that define a healthy system for this host, for example:
#
#   sshd.service
#   podman.service
#   nginx.service
